00:01:26.306 --> 00:01:29.220
in velkhe shtot, in velkhn land.

00:01:30.828 --> 00:01:32.577
koydem vel ikh makhn a shtikl hakdome.

00:01:33.039 --> 00:01:37.134
ikh red yidish vayl dos iz geven di shprakh

00:01:37.713 --> 00:01:44.340
fun di zeks, mertsn fun di zeks milyon vos zenen farbrent gevorn, dos iz geven di shprakh iz geven ammerstn yidish.

00:01:44.497 --> 00:01:48.238
derfar vil ikh, vil ikh gebn der intervyu oyf yidish.

00:01:48.986 --> 00:01:51.596
ikh bin geborn in a shtetl vos se heyst KEREZKY.

00:01:52.833 --> 00:01:54.009
a kleyn shtetl,

00:01:52.968 --> 00:01:55.404
