oyf english.

00:01:56.934 --> 00:02:02.885
R.E.Z- Z.K.Y.

00:02:03.903 --> 00:02:08.094
un dos iz gevezn in der Tshekhoslovakay eyne fun di REPUBLICS,

00:02:08.094 --> 00:02:10.867
se geven fir REPUBLICS, dos hot geheysn Karpate-Rus.

00:02:11.328 --> 00:02:15.187
ven ikh bin geborn iz dort geven, dey gegnt iz geven der Tshekhoslovakay.

00:02:15.328 --> 00:02:16.993
shpeter bay der milkhome,

00:02:17.167 --> 00:02:21.549
der tsveyter velt milkhome, iz es aribergegangen tsu di un- tsu di ungarn.

00:02:23.445 --> 00:02:27.810
ikh bin geborn in toyznt nayn hundert eyn un tsvontsik, dem akhtstn november,

00:02:29.402 --> 00:02:32.215
tsu mayn tate vos er hot geheysn Moyshe Vays,

00:02:32.473 --> 00:02:34.661
un mayn mame hot geheysn Sheyndl

00:02:36.303 --> 00:02:39.335
fun der als,

00:02:39.763 --> 00:02:42.373
fun der heym oys hot zi geheysn Shteynberger.

00:02:42.699 --> 00:02:44.246
un me hot zi gerufn UNK.

00:02:46.698 --> 00:02:50.906
iz vos ir kent ir dertseyln funem tatn,

00:02:50.906 --> 00:02:52.498
un dernokh dem fun di muter?

00:02:52.622 --> 00:02:53.342
yo.

00:02:55.355 --> 00:03:01.408
undzer mishpokhe iz gevezn fun doyre-doyres a khasidishe mishpokhe.

00:03:02.392 --> 00:03:05.086
mir hobn geshtamt zi- ziditshoyver khasidim.

00:03:06.594 --> 00:03:13.490
mayn elter elter zeyde iz gekumen ahin alts sheliekh funem Ziditshoyver rebn,

00:03:13.935 --> 00:03:16.157
se nokh nisht geven keyn minyen dort in shtetl.

00:03:17.090 --> 00:03:18.569
un er hot im gebentsht,

00:03:19.419 --> 00:03:27.108
er hot im gezogt, "YEVOREKHEKHO VE- VEHEY BROKHO,"

00:03:27.570 --> 00:03:30.399
s'iz geven parshes Lekh-Lekho, un se take azoy gevezn.

00:03:30.489 --> 00:03:32.863
di mishpokhe hot zikh shnel farmert.

00:03:33.425 --> 00:03:37.368
yeder eyner hot gehat a zeks zibn kinder, un eyner hot tsvey tekhter.

00:03:38.032 --> 00:03:43.460
un azoy az se gevezn shoyn in mayne tsaytn, iz shoyn gevezn di mishpokhe getseylt

00:03:44.090 --> 00:03:46.261
a genoye tsvey hundert mitglider.

00:03:47.263 --> 00:03:52.117
azoy hot dos gantse shtetl, dos rov shtetl iz geven Vays, hot geheysn, di mishpokhe hot geheysn Vays.

00:03:52.747 --> 00:03:59.744
un deys vos ikh heys Levanoni, dos iz a andere mayse vos ikh hob geen- geendert dem nomen, ober mayn originaln nomen iz Vays.

00:04:00.932 --> 00:04:03.289
mayn mame iz geven fun an andere shtetl,

00:04:02.535 --> 00:04:06.073
vos hot gemakht der foter, voser voser fakh hot er gehat, der foter?

00:04:06.422 --> 00:04:09.077
se geven ayngefirt dort in der gantser gegnt,

00:04:09.690 --> 00:04:12.131
me hot gelernt in di yeshive biz tsu der khasene,

00:04:12.592 --> 00:04:17.025
un nokh di yeshive hot men khasene gehat, me hot gekrign a bisl nadn, me hot zikh geefnt a gesheftl.

00:04:17.216 --> 00:04:18.763
azoy iz geven ayngefirt.

00:04:18.482 --> 00:04:20.214
der foter hot gehat gesheft?

00:04:19.545 --> 00:04:21.365
a gesheft, yo, er hot gehat a,

00:04:20.422 --> 00:04:21.581
vos a gesheft?

00:04:21.365 --> 00:04:29.653
a gesheft, me hot es gerufn UNK dos heyst ales hot men gehaltn, gehaltn, esnvarg, kleydung, hitn, vos ir vilt, vayl se geven a kleyn shtetl.

00:04:29.130 --> 00:04:30.997
parnose iz geven fun dem?

00:04:30.442 --> 00:04:34.558
yo se geven parnose, un se geven interesant, me hot gevoynt in dem zelbn hoyz,

00:04:35.458 --> 00:04:37.798
in dos gesheft iz oykh geven in zelbn hoyz.

00:04:37.854 --> 00:04:46.770
un me hot oyfgemakht di tir iz geven a glok, se hot a klung geton, hot men gevust az se kumt arayn a koyne un me iz bald arayngegangen in gesheft arayn. az se geven mer koynim iz gezesn in gesheft, azoy,

00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.446
vayl se nisht geven tsu fil gesheftn.

00:04:48.468 --> 00:04:49.525
un di muter?

00:04:50.105 --> 00:04:53.846
mayn mame iz gevezn in an andere shtot, fun Orsheve,

00:04:56.147 --> 00:04:58.031
der zeyde iz geven a groyser oysher,

00:04:58.475 --> 00:05:01.898
er hot gehat a mil, vos hot gemoln mel,

00:05:01.901 --> 00:05:07.701
un se geven a kleyne ELECTRIC COMPANY, vos hobn gegebn ELECTRIC far di shtetl,

00:05:08.482 --> 00:05:10.029
un er hot gehat oykhet

00:05:10.727 --> 00:05:13.860
oyl pres, me hot gemakht shemen.

00:05:14.810 --> 00:05:18.689
shpeter iz er a bisl aropgegangen, ober er hot vayter

00:05:18.689 --> 00:05:24.980
un er iz geven aza groyser oysher ober er hot vayter ongefirt, dos gesheft.

00:05:25.526 --> 00:05:27.933
un brider, shvester?

00:05:29.019 --> 00:05:35.021
ze'mir geven se, ze'mir gevezn zeks geshvister.

00:05:36.410 --> 00:05:38.649
gedenkt dem nom- ir gedenkt di nemen?

00:05:36.444 --> 00:05:39.223
ikh, yo, ikh bin der eltster.

00:05:39.262 --> 00:05:39.999
ye.

00:05:40.460 --> 00:05:44.133
un mayn r- gantser nomen iz Yisroel Dov.

00:05:45.472 --> 00:05:49.584
ikh bin geven der bekhor, ikh bin nitsl gevorn.

00:05:49.978 --> 00:05:54.242
mayn bruder hot geheysn Aron, er iz oykh nitsl gevorn,

00:05:54.483 --> 00:05:57.088
un do in Erets Yisroel iz er geven in di HAGANA,

00:05:57.116 --> 00:05:59.169
un er iz geharget gevorn lebn Khulon,

00:06:01.807 --> 00:06:03.945
se dort gevezn TSALAFIM,

00:06:04.305 --> 00:06:08.040
un zey hobn punkt arayngetrofn in harts arayn, er iz geven in gantsn tsvontsik yor alt.

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:10.981
a shtarker gezunter mentsh un er iz nebekh nifter gevorn.

00:06:10.076 --> 00:06:11.775
andere brider un shvester?

00:06:11.122 --> 00:06:13.204
tsveyter bruder hot geheysn Avrom,

00:06:13.204 --> 00:06:17.276
er iz oykh gekumen aher oyf Erets Yisroel, nokh der milkhome,

00:06:17.585 --> 00:06:20.009
er hot do khasene gehat, er iz geven a TAYAKH.

00:06:21.922 --> 00:06:26.996
un bay di fertsik yor iz er nifter gevorn, fun a makhle,

00:06:27.744 --> 00:06:29.358
un er hot gelozt tsvey zin.

00:06:29.465 --> 00:06:33.037
eyner heyst Moyshe un eyner heyst Aron, zey gefinen zikh in Erets Yisroel.

00:06:33.414 --> 00:06:38.015
Moyshe hot dray kinder, in Khulon voynt er, un Aron

00:06:38.426 --> 00:06:43.753
halt er hitst khasene hobn, er iz shoyn an elterer bokher fun fertsik yor, ober er halt in yetst khasene hobn,

00:06:44.180 --> 00:06:45.862
er hot nokh nisht keyn kinder.

00:06:46.053 --> 00:06:49.979
ir hot shtudirt in a shule, oder nor in kheyder?

00:06:52.297 --> 00:06:54.418
ikh hob gelernt in kheyder.

00:06:55.082 --> 00:06:56.426
vifl, vi lang?

00:06:57.107 --> 00:06:58.350
biz vifl yor?

00:06:57.107 --> 00:07:01.860
biz, di gantse tsayt bin ikh gevezn in kheyder un nokh dem gegangen in yeshive.

00:07:02.186 --> 00:07:04.192
biz tsum aveknemen, ober in der zayt,

00:07:02.861 --> 00:07:04.239
UNK

00:07:04.192 --> 00:07:07.260
ober in der zayt hob ikh nokh gelernt in sforim.

00:07:07.923 --> 00:07:11.363
ikh hob gelernt kheshbn fun sforim, bukhhaltung fun sforim,

00:07:11.363 --> 00:07:14.212
khimye gelernt fun sforim, fun bikher,

00:07:14.859 --> 00:07:25.451
un un ikh hob gehat a khaver vos er iz gegangen in der HIGH SCHOOL,

00:07:25.777 --> 00:07:29.940
ober mayn visnshaft iz nisht geven veyniker vi zayn visnshaft.

00:07:30.114 --> 00:07:34.946
vayl ikh hob alts gekh- gezukht bikher ikh zol kenen di funde- fundamentale,

00:07:34.974 --> 00:07:39.778
fundamentalishe sforim tsi tsi far visnshaft.

00:07:40.172 --> 00:07:43.996
un ir gedenkt di nomen fun di yeshive?

00:07:43.952 --> 00:07:44.638
yo.

00:07:44.627 --> 00:07:45.938
vi heyst di yeshive?

00:07:45.453 --> 00:07:47.422
se do afile a bild oykh fun di yeshive.

00:07:47.597 --> 00:07:48.351
aha.

00:07:48.373 --> 00:07:52.417
do a s- a seyfer, se do aza seyfer fun RABANIM DEARYE,

00:07:51.208 --> 00:07:53.869
di yeshive iz di ven,

00:07:52.997 --> 00:07:54.741
der kheyder iz geven a kheyder.

00:07:54.752 --> 00:07:56.242
un di yeshive,

00:07:55.517 --> 00:07:57.074
un di yeshive iz nokh vos,

00:07:56.242 --> 00:08:02.491
di yeshive, di yeshive iz geven nokhn kheyder, nokh fertsn yor, bin ikh geven, di ershte yeshive bin ikh geven in Selush.

00:08:03.392 --> 00:08:07.774
dort iz geven der Spinker rebe. Reb Yitskhok Ayzik Vays.

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:11.987
un der Spinker rebe, der hayntiker,

00:08:11.987 --> 00:08:16.514
der hayntiker iz oykh a Spinker rebe, dos iz geven far im an elter zeyde.

00:08:16.740 --> 00:08:17.905
yetst,

00:08:18.579 --> 00:08:21.074
un dernokh dem hob ikh gelernt in Naytre,

00:08:21.074 --> 00:08:22.691
NITRE, dos iz geven Slovakay.

00:08:23.220 --> 00:08:26.522
bay rav Ungar. er iz geven,

00:08:25.430 --> 00:08:26.406
vos hot ir geler-

00:08:26.406 --> 00:08:28.176
vos hot ir gelernt bay rav Ungar?

00:08:27.894 --> 00:08:32.397
oykh a yeshive, vos men lernt in a yeshive? in yeshive lernt men nor gemore, toysfes,

00:08:32.397 --> 00:08:35.161
Yoyre-Deye, un VEKHULU.

00:08:36.298 --> 00:08:41.760
vos kent ir itster mit dertseyln fun yi- fun di yidishe kehile

00:08:42.339 --> 00:08:46.783
in ayer shtot? ver iz geven? se geven a rov, se geven a shoykhet?

00:08:46.783 --> 00:08:53.420
se geven a moyel, tsi tsi me hot gedavnt in shabes, un vos kent ir dertseyln?

00:08:49.055 --> 00:08:49.961
yo.

00:08:52.818 --> 00:08:55.398
koydem iz gevezn iz gevezn,

00:08:55.316 --> 00:08:57.251
vifl yidn zenen geven dort?

00:08:55.398 --> 00:08:57.034
hundert protsent,

00:08:57.034 --> 00:08:59.377
hundert fuftsik mishpokhes in dey tsayt.

00:09:00.851 --> 00:09:06.670
un un der rov iz gevezn reb Khanokh Henekh Meyer.

00:09:06.707 --> 00:09:12.624
er iz gevezn a a vunder re- rebe ruft men dos on, er hot gevayzn, gevizn farshidene mofsim.

00:09:13.203 --> 00:09:14.075
se iz,

00:09:14.503 --> 00:09:19.897
un er hot do a zun, zayn zun iz geven der Kurhayzer rov,

00:09:20.004 --> 00:09:21.990
ikh hob gelernt mit zayn zun oykh,

00:09:22.873 --> 00:09:27.981
un er lebt shoyn oykh nisht der Kurhayzer rov, gefi- gefint zikh do zayn eyniklekh, er iz geven der rov,

00:09:29.471 --> 00:09:31.136
er iz geshtamt fun Galitsye.

00:09:31.243 --> 00:09:32.857
er hot zikh dort bazetst,

00:09:33.150 --> 00:09:37.701
er iz geven a shvoger mitn Satmarer rov, dos iz geven a bavuster rov in dey tsaytn.

00:09:37.841 --> 00:09:38.612
ye.

