yeder yid hot khasene gehat, oyfgemakht a gesheftl.

00:10:22.020 --> 00:10:24.900
un un fun dem hot men gelebt.

00:10:24.905 --> 00:10:27.397
un vi iz geven der YAKHAS tsvishn,

00:10:28.112 --> 00:10:31.481
dos iz geven ungarn, oder tshekh- di ungarn,

00:10:30.508 --> 00:10:34.822
in mayne tsaytn, biz tsu dem tsveyte iz gevezn dort Tshekhay.

00:10:34.895 --> 00:10:38.433
ikh bin gegangen in der tshekhishe shul un oykh in der in di ukrainishe shul.

00:10:38.557 --> 00:10:42.365
vayl mayn tate un der zeyde hot gevolt az ikh zol kenen oykh ukrainish, oykh tshekhish.

00:10:42.489 --> 00:10:46.567
un di goyim vos hobn gevoynt arum un arum, dos iz geven tshekhn oykhet, oder,

00:10:45.729 --> 00:10:48.187
der, arum un arum iz geven ales ukrainer.

00:10:47.990 --> 00:10:49.143
ales ukrainer.

00:10:48.615 --> 00:10:49.858
ukrainer iz geven.

00:10:49.143 --> 00:10:52.220
vi iz geven der YAKHAS tsvishn yidn un der,

00:10:52.665 --> 00:10:56.543
di yidishe kehile, se geven a mol pogromen, me hot a mol gere-

00:10:52.806 --> 00:10:53.773
se gevezn,

00:10:56.543 --> 00:11:00.928
me hot a mol geget a shto- a shtokh a yid, a UNK?

00:10:59.972 --> 00:11:01.941
pogromen iz keyn mol nisht gevezn.

